comment:
* Static utility class for constructing native interpolators to keep the
 * JNI simpler
 *
 * @hide

methods.name: public static long createNativeInterpolator(TimeInterpolator interpolator, long duration)
methods.comment:
* Create a native interpolator from the provided param generating a LUT variant if a native
     * implementation does not exist.

methods.name: public static native long createAccelerateDecelerateInterpolator()
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Accelerate/Decelerate

methods.name: public static native long createAccelerateInterpolator(float factor)
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Accelerate

methods.name: public static native long createAnticipateInterpolator(float tension)
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Anticipate

methods.name: public static native long createAnticipateOvershootInterpolator(float tension)
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Anticipate with Overshoot

methods.name: public static native long createBounceInterpolator()
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Bounce

methods.name: public static native long createCycleInterpolator(float cycles)
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Cycle

methods.name: public static native long createDecelerateInterpolator(float factor)
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Decelerate

methods.name: public static native long createLinearInterpolator()
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Linear interpolation

methods.name: public static native long createOvershootInterpolator(float tension)
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for Overshoot

methods.name: public static native long createPathInterpolator(float[] x, float[] y)
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for along traveling along a Path

methods.name: public static native long createLutInterpolator(float[] values)
methods.comment: Creates a specialized native interpolator for LUT
